{
  "stem": "1929.2",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We're looking for cigarette butts, collect cigarette butts, because we could take the tobacco out of it, and we could get some money for it.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I have, I have no memory of my mother, outside of the one in Sulejow when she throws herself on top of me.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I have some glimpses of a memory of her living with us in the ghetto, and her going to the bathroom.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That's the only memory I have of my mother.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I have not been able to restore any memory.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I thought I was much younger then, but actually, my mother lived with me till, till, I was probably about, oh, at least 10 or 11.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And so, that would-- I would have, normally, I would have memories of my mother, but I have no memories of my mother.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Blank.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And she's not there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, you know, there were-- every few weeks, or maybe every day, there was new proclamations by the German authorities.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You couldn't own property.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You could only have so much money on you.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You couldn't do business with the Christians.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Like, if you're a Jewish doctor, you couldn't treat Christians.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And what I remember is that there was-- that the setting up of a Jewish council.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I actually remember that, outside of reading it in the book, that there was.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "There were people who-- within the ghetto, Jewish people, generally the people who had been the leaders of the community before-- were in charge of the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And they are the ones who dealt with the Germans.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "All the orders from the Germans came through the Germans to the Judens-- something Judens, Strauss or something.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Jewish council.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, or Jewish elders.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
